{"tid":2486441,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港台：日本決定將福島縣核廢水排出大海惹反對","createTime":"2021-04-13T01:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:52.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ee85b7014bef96cfe0c4aa038e53b89d4be23a5c","tid":2486441,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年是日本311大地震十周年，當年的地震和海嘯，除了造成重大傷亡，亦引發福島核事故。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府今日決定，在大約兩年後，將經稀釋的核廢水排入大海，但建議引起漁民組織強烈反對。<strong>中國和南韓亦表示關注</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n有意見認為，<strong>此舉將衝擊執政自民黨的民望，以至是東京奧運的舉辦。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585460-20210413.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585460-20210413.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=aa328da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585460-20210413.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7731516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585460-20210413.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0c6741c5167ff04fd5b87096ceb7cfd398027c41","tid":2486441,"uid":259901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"做乜要干涉日本內政？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ffd1bdcb731317d56152ecbaf6b68ddffa6eed","tid":2486441,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"廢水係支那不可分割既一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd50cf64651669ce8c74f0c24ecab243b0508da6","tid":2486441,"uid":267494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"日本：展現體制自信，堅決捍衛自身發展道路，倒核廢水純屬日本內政，外國無權干預<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4